      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: PTP_Procure To Pay
Process Group: PM_Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process:PM-090-040 Create Supplier Contract
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-FAB8AB8B-3662-4722-9FFB-C28132ADC209" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description- 
Enter Information such as service price/rate, quantity or value and validity period along with commercial terms, clauses, quality certification information, accurate official notification address in a database holding both parties accountable while providing ability to negotiate, redline contracts, etc. supporting contract lifecycle management, compliance and risk mitigation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8CD06228-D9D0-4778-AD7E-000141ACEC1F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>*Manual step to enter price to legal contracts
*Add Awarded price if needed</text>
      </textAnnotation>
